<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-nervous-about">(be) nervous about</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>对……神经紧张/害怕/胆怯/焦虑不安</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We were all nervous about the approaching examinations.
我们当时都对即将到来的考试感到紧张不安。</p><footer>人教④ – 4</footer></div></div>